The paper focuses on testing and identifying faults in Deep Neural Networks (DNNs), which is a topic that falls under the broad category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the importance of ensuring the safety and reliability of DNNs, which is a concern in the field of Software Engineering (cs.SE) and Cybersecurity (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper evaluates the effectiveness of the proposed approach on image classification tasks, which is a common application of Computer Vision (cs.CV).
